(firstQuint)Acupuncture for CIPN in Breast Cancer Patients.

 Ideally 10 patients experiencing peripheral neuropathy due to chemotherapy from breast cancer treatment will be included in this study.

They will receive 16 total acupuncture treatments over 10 weeks including various points based off of research and classical text and scalp acupuncture.

.

